subsection.def:
amidships
                    (船舯) means at the middle of the length
                (L);

area
                    (面積) in relation to a ship shall be
                calculated in all cases to moulded lines;

IOPP Certificate (IOPP證書) means a certificate issued under regulation 7(1)(a);
                        (L.N. 47 of
                2016)

IOPPE Certificate (IOPPE證書) means a certificate issued under regulation 7EB;
                        (L.N. 154 of
                2022)

sea
                    (海、海域)
                includes any estuary or arm of the sea;

volume
                    (容積) in relation to a ship shall be
                calculated in all cases to moulded lines;

